{"tid":1310230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球皇迪列治1月早想去祖記 轉會有望本週確定","createTime":"2019-07-12T14:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T02:51:15.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee241db51c69b63553261bd2d6807aa5ad07e283","tid":1310230,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"據荷蘭媒體《Algemeen Dagbald》消息，迪列治（M.de Ligt）自今年1月以來就一直熱衷於轉投祖雲達斯，並因此對其他球會的邀約興趣冷淡。<br />\n<br />\n　　迪列治今夏吸引了祖雲達斯、巴黎聖日耳門、巴塞隆拿在內的眾多豪門的關注。《荷蘭電訊報》最新消息指出，隨著祖雲達斯將對迪列治的報價提高至6700萬歐元，阿積士預計會為這位荷蘭國腳開綠燈放行。<br />\n<br />\n　　而荷蘭媒體《Algemeen Dagbald》則指出，迪列治其實自今年1月以來就一直嚮往加盟祖雲達斯。據悉，這家門戶網站同時指出，迪列治的轉會已接近完成，目前只剩少數細節有待三方共同敲定。迪列治的正式官宣有望在本週末公佈，球員可能會在週六亮相祖雲達斯。"},{"pid":"b07103367752f06b3a89e4714eb19546b65bc4c3","tid":1310230,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aff025d14586852b729465a49dc78a850fecc04","tid":1310230,"uid":268580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:44:27.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c844b2f03717b1eca6cb6491d8fb4533e1b0f142","tid":1310230,"uid":234509,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:00:19.000Z","msg":"煩夠未<br />\n梅斯達菲級數<br />\n吹撚大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28945c1141e2511c35d3c0b20643c21f924c20f8","tid":1310230,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c844b2f03717b1eca6cb6491d8fb4533e1b0f142","tid":1310230,"uid":234509,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:00:19.000Z","msg":"煩夠未<br />\n梅斯達菲級數<br />\n吹撚大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"咁迪列治的確係近年最轟動既球王轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用梅屎同佢比 你hi大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm